{"tid":931901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你咩！條仆街真係想害死人【鐵騎奔馳單車徑】","createTime":"2018-12-07T10:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T11:05:08.000Z","uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"88a29af3e32357c7f6b5f20a8e0090c8dd339028","tid":931901,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:52:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181207/bkn-20181207181941920-1207_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181207%2Fbkn-20181207181941920-1207_00822_001.html&d=OG2FKvExQ3NIMvp287CNawRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b56d72eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181207/bkn-20181207181941920-1207_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\nLINK有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nEA1UMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnEA1UMx.jpg&h=ff2d00f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>爭取路權？鐵騎單車徑疾馳　隧道有人隨時撞？</strong><br />\n<br />\n電單車都係單車？近日太和有電單車司機直踩單車徑，快速行駛，令網民怒斥︰「無法無天」。<br />\n<br />\n影片於星期五（7日）上載至Facebook群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」，片段所見，有男子駛着電單車，沿太和汀太路近大埔游泳池對開一段單車徑疾馳，響起隆隆的引擎聲。<br />\n<br />\n當時雖未有其他單車使用者，但電單車在駛經隧道口及彎位時亦未見減速，引來途人側目。<br />\n<br />\n片段惹起網民憤怒：「佢以為自己都係單車呀」、「遲早害死人」、「隧道有單車出嚟就死」，又指已向政府熱線「1823」投訴事件。有區議員更留言指，已幫忙向警方反映事件。"},{"pid":"956915d124fac724000dbf14ebde77802b843c64","tid":931901,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}